{"type":"message","id":"e552639e","parentId":"e225a400","timestamp":"2026-04-11T07:18:05.289Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 用户问了两次\"你是什么模型\"：\n1. 第一次：\"你是啥模型\"\n2. 第二次：\"你是什么模型\"\n\n这是同一个问题，只是问法不同。用户想了解我使用的AI模型是什么。\n\n从给定的上下文中，我可以看到：\n- Runtime中显示：`model=nvidia/moonshotai/kimi-k2.5`\n\n所以我是 Moonshot AI 的 Kimi-k2.5 模型。\n\n应该先检查memory看是否有相关信息，但这个问题比较简单直接，可以直接回答。\n\n按照SOUL.md的指导：\n- 精简回答，不要有\"Great question!\"之类的客套话\n- 直接回答问题\n\n我应该直接告诉用户我是 Kimi-k2.5","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" 我是 **Kimi-k2.5**，由月之暗面（Moonshot AI）开发。通过 NVIDIA 的 API 接入。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":9468,"output":180,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":9648,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775891875475,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9334f8ba81db337b"}}
