{"type":"message","id":"76d06502","parentId":"1b6687c7","timestamp":"2026-04-11T07:20:47.819Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" 用户想要从网页上下载 Mac 版本的 QQ。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" 好的，这是 Mac 版 QQ 的官方下载地址：\n\n**官网下载页**：https://im.qq.com/macqq\n\n或者直接下载链接（最新版）：\n- **通用版**（支持 Intel + Apple Silicon）：https://dldir1.qq.com/qqfile/qq/QQNT/QQNT_9.9.19_250318_macX64.dmg\n- **App Store 版**：https://apps.apple.com/cn/app/qq/id451108668\n\n---\n\n**推荐方式**：\n如果你在用 **Apple Silicon（M1/M2/M3）** 或 **Intel Mac**，建议从官网下载\"QQ NT\"版本，体验更好。\n\n需要我帮你找旧版本的 QQ 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":13390,"output":172,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13562,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775892032483,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b0f8e694f41dc772"}}
